{"tid":409572,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel將推出8核心桌上型Core i7處理器","createTime":"2017-09-22T07:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T08:03:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8c63f99d02bdc7143123b9cb59a9257b634e4f","tid":409572,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:30:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">AMD今年推出的Ryzen系列處理器憑著核心數的優勢，在多工運算方面的應用的確是相當出色，然而也因為這樣的情況，讓Intel近來也開始動作頻頻，先在Computex發表了針對專業應用的18核心Core i9處理器，緊接著再針對一般消費型市場再度發表了第八代Core處理器產品，並且在桌上型Core i7處理器系列中不僅會先推出6核12緒版本，預計在明年還會有一款8核16緒的Core i7處理器以及全新的Z390主機板。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201709/mobile01-e200b279f97178689b09d96ae62fb986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201709%2Fmobile01-e200b279f97178689b09d96ae62fb986.jpg&h=a8a38f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201709/mobile01-3d50058cd33944bf530eb71bc31ac9bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201709%2Fmobile01-3d50058cd33944bf530eb71bc31ac9bf.jpg&h=16fc5cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/newsdetail/22486/intel-cannon-lake-8th-gen-eight-core-i7-z390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobile01.com%2Fnewsdetail%2F22486%2Fintel-cannon-lake-8th-gen-eight-core-i7-z390&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNT0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8a246ee5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobile01.com/newsdetail/22486/intel-cannon-lake-8th-gen-eight-core-i7-z390</a><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://benchlife.info/coffee-lake-more-than-two-core-is-only-anecdotes-intel-may-be-brewing-8-core-products/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbenchlife.info%2Fcoffee-lake-more-than-two-core-is-only-anecdotes-intel-may-be-brewing-8-core-products%2F&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNT0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=adb93566\" target=\"_blank\">https://benchlife.info/coffee-lake-more-than-two-core-is-only-anecdotes-intel-may-be-brewing-8-core-products/</a></div>"},{"pid":"d7d76a0b8715aeedc7d1ea81a6d3a50e9c6cdb82","tid":409572,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"aa4f66f2723d93a0e0bba7c54e77ff6fbde607e2","tid":409572,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"Intel 不了<br />\n又係垃圾矽脂"}]}